  "detailed_description": "The Wormaid is an indie puzzle game where you play as an exceedingly long worm-like creature seeking to unravel the mystery of your lost children. The puzzles follow the theme of space-filling (covering all tiles on a grid); however, the order and pattern of filling can reveal special symbols in the world that become a stepping path for the strange inhabitants of the game.<br><br><strong>Meet The Bishop</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/9ef07bbde44fe14a1c40e047cb647939.poster.avif?t=1670300221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/9ef07bbde44fe14a1c40e047cb647939.webm?t=1670300221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/9ef07bbde44fe14a1c40e047cb647939.mp4?t=1670300221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore The Castle</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/8ce89fa210c27f4bcb781ce24bc08a08.poster.avif?t=1670300221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/8ce89fa210c27f4bcb781ce24bc08a08.webm?t=1670300221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478240/extras/8ce89fa210c27f4bcb781ce24bc08a08.mp4?t=1670300221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Meet The Rook</strong><br><br><strong>Be The Worm</strong>",
